```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Healthcare Survey</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
       .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
        }
       .prize-section {
            background-color: #e0f7fa;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
       .prize-section h2 {
            color: #009688;
        }
       .testimonial-section {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
       .testimonial-section h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
       .testimonial {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
       .testimonial h3 {
            color: #009688;
        }
       .testimonial p {
            color: #666;
        }
       .survey-form {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
       .survey-form label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
       .survey-form input[type="text"],.survey-form input[type="email"],.survey-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
       .survey-form button {
            background-color: #009688;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
       .survey-form button:hover {
            background-color: #00796b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Healthcare Survey</h1>
        <p>Join our survey and stand a chance to win a FREE healthcare package worth $500!</p>

        <div class="prize-section">
            <h2>Win a FREE Healthcare Package</h2>
            <p>By participating in our survey, you can win a FREE healthcare package valued at $500. This includes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Fitness Class Pass</li>
                <li>Healthy Meal Box</li>
                <li>Health Monitoring Devices</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

